---
title: Double Korean Ginger Beef & Corn Slaw Bowl with Fried Egg & Spring Onion
description: This sizzling hot Korean-style beef from the pan is a delight unparalleled. Delicious marinated beef and the joy of simplicity are winners in this dish. Topped off with a fried egg, this dish is a brilliant twist on a weeknight dinner.

